{
  "texts": [
    "In our work, our rewriter is also LLM-based, leveraging LLM's self refinement through feedback and reasoning.",
    "The key difference is that we have to take into consideration the cost and latency, which demands fewer output tokens, while ensuring the mitigation performance.",
    "3 Hallucination Taxonomy and GPT4-based detection",
    "We started with developing a hallucination taxonomy by manually analyzing various hallucinated model outputs, mainly from some internal summarization systems, which is based on a state-of-theart encoder-decoder model about 1B parameters.",
    "We randomly collected 500 samples from production systems and benchmark systems, including ChatGPT, and manually identified the 34 hallucinated outputs (two of the authors)."
  ]
}